%body
  %header.head
    .head__main
      .head__main__top
        %h1.head__main__top__icon
          = link_to image_tag("/assets/logo/logo.png",class:"head__main__top__icon__img"), "/"
        %form.head__main__top__search{"accept-charset" => "UTF-8", :action => "#", :method => "get"}
          %input.head__main__top__search__input{:name => "key", :placeholder => "キーワードから探す"}/
          %button.head__main__top__search__btn{:type => "submit"}
            =image_tag  "/assets/icon/icon-search.png",class:"head__main__top__search__btn__img"
      .head__main__bottom
        %ul.head__main__bottom__left
          %li.head__main__bottom__left__item
            = link_to "カテゴリー", "#",{class: "head__main__bottom__left__item__link"}
          %li.head__main__bottom__left__item
            = link_to "ブランド", "#",{class: "head__main__bottom__left__item__link"}
        %ul.head__main__bottom__right
          %li.head__main__bottom__right__item
            = link_to "ログイン", "#",{class: "head__main__bottom__left__item__link"}
          %li.head__main__bottom__right__item
            = link_to "新規会員登録", "#",{class: "head__main__bottom__left__item__link"}
  .main
    .main__intro
      .main__intro__content
        %h2.main__intro__content__subtitle
          %br/
          人生を変えるフリマアプリ
        %p.main__intro__content__text
          FURIMAはだれでもかんたんに出品・購入できる
          %br/
          フリマアプリです
        .main__intro__content__btn
          = link_to image_tag("/assets/Download_on_the_App_Store_Badge_US-UK_RGB_blk_092917.svg",class:"aBtn"), "#"
          = link_to image_tag("/assets/google-play-badge.png",class:"gBtn"), "#"
      .picture
    .main__reason
      %h2.main__reason__subtitle
        FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
      %ul.main__reason__lists
        %li.main__reason__list
          .main__reason__list__pict
            %span.main__reason__list__pict__number 1
            =image_tag  "/assets/pict/pict-reason-01.jpg"
          %h3.main__reason__list__text
            %span 3分
            ですぐに出品
          %p.main__reason__list__description
            スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
        %li.main__reason__list
          .main__reason__list__pict
            %span.main__reason__list__pict__number 2
            =image_tag  "/assets/pict/pict-reason-02.jpg"
          %h3.main__reason__list__text
            %span シンプル
            で使いやすい
          %p.main__reason__list__description
            めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
        %li.main__reason__list
          .main__reason__list__pict
            %span.main__reason__list__pict__number 3
            =image_tag  "/assets/pict/pict-reason-03.jpg"
          %h3.main__reason__list__text
            手数料
            %span 業界最安
          %p.main__reason__list__description
            最大3%でお得に出品&amp;購入！
    .main__dwlink
      .main__dwlink__inner
        %h2.main__dwlink__inner__subtitle 会員数日本一位
        %p.main__dwlink__inner__text
          FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気。
          %br/
          出品・購入回数も業界最多です！
          %br/
          ほしかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません。
        .main__dwlink__inner__btn
          = link_to image_tag("/assets/Download_on_the_App_Store_Badge_US-UK_RGB_blk_092917.svg",class:"aBtn"), "#"
          = link_to image_tag("/assets/google-play-badge.png",class:"gBtn"), "#"
    .main__features
      %h2.main__features__head FURIMAの特徴
      .main__features__items
        .main__features__item
          .main__features__item__img
            =image_tag  "/assets/icon/icon-01.png"
          %h3.main__features__item__subtitle 簡単に売り買いできる
          %p.main__features__item__detail
            スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
        .main__features__item
          .main__features__item__img
            =image_tag  "/assets/icon/icon-03.png"
          %h3.main__features__item__subtitle 売上金は即日振込みに対応
          %p.main__features__item__detail
            午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
        .main__features__item
          .main__features__item__img
            =image_tag  "/assets/icon/icon-04.png"
          %h3.main__features__item__subtitle 様々な支払いに対応
          %p.main__features__item__detail
            お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。
